&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ years of experience in disputes, fraud operations, or 1 year of general banking experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of Regulation E and card network dispute rules&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience communicating with customers via phone and email in a professional, empathetic manner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to identify patterns in dispute, fraud, or risk activity and escalate concerns when necessary&lt;/li&gt;
