&lt;li&gt;Stream-processing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Machine learning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participating in code reviews and contributing to a culture of engineering quality&lt;/li&gt;
